    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Zend_Test_PHPUnit_ControllerTestCase::assertNotRedirect causes an "undefined index: location" error notice in 1.12.0rc1.</p>

<p>It produces an E_NOTICE error which fails test suite.</p>

<p>To reproduce:</p>

<p>1) Create zf app with zf tool</p>

<p>2) Add: $this-&gt;assertNotRedirect(); to the end of the method testIndexAction() in file: tests/application/controllers/IndexController.php</p>

<p>3) run tests</p>

